ght from the single-dish data. We emphasize the importance of\ndirect submillimeter high-resolution studies on faint SMGs, which could be the\ndominant population of the high-z star formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2011 21:00:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-12-15"}
